Package: RTextCleaner
Title: A Toolkit for Cleaning and Processing Text Data in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Skylar", "Shao", email = "skylar.shao@example.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: RTextCleaner provides functions for text preprocessing, including 
    text normalization, sentiment analysis, noise removal, and code-text separation.
    It improves text quality for NLP tasks and data analysis.
